    "description": "Depth-2 helper: takes {query, threshold}; under threshold -> one Cognee retrieval, over -> decompose once (L2, cap 5) + retrieve each + combine. Calls only 'Cognee Retrieve One', so depth is hard-capped at 2 (no recursion).",
